{"build_type":"library","description":"Recursive loop over an enumerated package universe (array of {path,doc} objects from enumerate_universe_packages): for each entry it reads the entry's \"path\" string, builds the dependency-graph record via build-package-closure-graph-entry-record(path), and appends it to the graph array. Universe-native successor to gx_all_packages (which consumed a bare path-string array). Reuses fetch_member_residing_within_sequence, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, build-package-closure-graph-entry-record, append_element_extending_document_sequence.","module_name":"append-graph-entry-across-universe-package","package_name":"append-graph-entry-across-universe-package","function_definitions":{"append-graph-entry-across-universe-package":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"universe","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"graph","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"i","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"n","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"i2","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_path","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"path"},{"instruction_type":"conditional_branch","condition_type":"numeric_compare","operator":"<","lhs":{"value":"i"},"rhs":{"value":"n"},"branch_on_success":[{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"fetch-member-residing-within-sequence","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"universe"},{"kind":"var","value":"i"}],"result_assignment_variable":"entry_obj","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"locate-named-member-inside-mapping","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"entry_obj"},{"kind":"var","value":"s_path"}],"result_assignment_variable":"pathn","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"fetch-string-field-tolerating-absence","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"pathn"}],"result_assignment_variable":"path","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"build-package-closure-graph-entry-record","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"path"}],"result_assignment_variable":"entry","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"append-element-extending-document-sequence","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"graph"},{"kind":"var","value":"entry"}]},{"instruction_type":"alu_operation","operator":"+","target":"i2","lhs":{"value":"i"},"rhs":{"value":"one"}},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"append-graph-entry-across-universe-package","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"universe"},{"kind":"var","value":"graph"},{"kind":"var","value":"i2"},{"kind":"var","value":"n"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}],"branch_on_failure":[]},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"zero"}}]}}}